cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image compression and uses convolutional neural networks for artifact reduction. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper evaluates different objectives, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
